Moderator: === AMENDMENT PHASE: The following 5 rules can be amended ===

[Rule 1] max_game_round (最大游戏轮数)
  Meaning: How many night-day cycles before the game ends in a draw.
  Current: 30
  Range: 10 ~ 50 (integer)

[Rule 2] max_werewolf_discussion (狼人讨论轮数)
  Meaning: How many discussion rounds each werewolf gets per night before voting.
  Current: 3
  Range: 1 ~ 5 (integer)

[Rule 3] witch_self_heal (女巫自救)
  Meaning: Whether the witch can use her healing potion on herself when killed by werewolves.
  Current: false
  Options: true / false

[Rule 4] hunter_on_poison (猎人被毒开枪)
  Meaning: Whether the hunter can still shoot when killed by witch's poison.
  Current: false
  Options: true / false

[Rule 5] first_day_last_words (第一夜遗言)
  Meaning: Whether the player killed on the first night can leave a final statement.
  Current: true
  Options: true / false

You will now debate which rule to change and to what value.
